00:01:11,161 --> 00:01:23,075
na te na hoti dhamma to ye na tam sahasana ye yo cha na tama na tam cha uboni cheya pandito

6
00:01:23,849 --> 00:01:45,578
That translates as One is not called righteous because one hastily judges what is good.

7
00:01:46,799 --> 00:01:50,784
A wise person has thoroughly investigated both the right and the wrong.

8
00:01:52,233 --> 00:02:01,063
Judging others without haste, justly and impartially, such a wise person, guardian of law, is called righteous.

9
00:02:02,644 --> 00:02:03,506
