Now, the commentary says, just to add to that, something that perhaps is more attuned to us, it is very easy to judge others, to point out others' mistakes and bad qualities.

19
00:03:32,948 --> 00:03:36,993
Therefore, we have to be very thorough when we have to judge others.

20
00:03:37,794 --> 00:03:40,359
We have to listen to every possible point of view.

21
00:03:40,939 --> 00:03:44,504
