you can imagine listening to that and uh just to make just to sort of rub that in i thought i'd give you what they used to say in the 18th century uh the lord is that thou shalt return to the place whence thou camest and from thence to the place of execution where thou shalt hang by the neck till the body be dead dead dead and the lord have mercy on your soul

