being guilty and and and drain and dreading consequences because of this old conditioning then of course it's it's gone on too long it's not it's not proper to the situation there's no need for that it's only when we indulge those thoughts either allowing the mind to escape on a fantasy or to actually speak something or to do something which is prejudicial that then of course we should have a greater sense of shame and guilt

